description: Jean has apparently awoken inside a hospital with no memory of who she is. Unsure of how to use her powers, Jean unintentionally attacks the staff, and provokes a city wide panic. With this new knowledge of where Jean is, Cyclops and Emma head to her location to rescue her, however, they are not the only ones looking.
name: Shades of Grey

description: After the shocking events of last episode, Jean Grey is in the clutches of the Inner Circle; a shadowy organization with plans for the Phoenix Force. Dark plans that involve using it end the war between mutants and humans, permanently. Meanwhile, Mystique has kidnapped Senator Kelly and is impersonating him under the orders of Magneto. With this upper hand, Magneto plans to unleash an army of Sentinels upon his own city finally having the incentive he needs to bring the fight to the humans.
name: Foresight - Part 1

description: With the Inner Circle getting increasingly close to unlocking the barriers in Jean's mind that house the Phoenix and the Sentinel attack on Genosha underway, the X-Men have their work cut out for them. However, with things beginning to look grim, even for the future X-Men, can Wolverine lead them to victory? Or is the horrible future set in stone?
name: Foresight - Part 2

description:
Our heroes in the present are locked in a struggle with Magneto and the Sentinel army, while the future X-Men are taking a final stand against Master Mold. And of course, when things couldn't possibly get worse, the Phoenix Force is released and the fate of both mutant and human kind hangs in the balance.

Get ready for the finale of Wolverine and the X-Men.
name: Foresight - Part 3
